SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT CMON_YEAR, cast (sum(CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTAMAILVERIFSENT) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTATELVERIFSENT) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTAMAILVERIFRCVDOK) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTAMAILVERIFRCVDNOTOK) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTATELVERIFRCVDOK) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTATELVERIFRCVDNOTOK) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTNDEBTORSACTIVE) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTNMAILVERIFSENT) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTNTELVERIFSENT) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTNMAILVERIFRCVDOK) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTNMAILVERIFRCVDNOTOK) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTNTELVERIFRCVDOK) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTNTELVERIFRCVDNOTOK) as decimal (13,2)) FROM :1 where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR between :4 and :5 and CMON_MONTH between :6 and :7 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':8' group by CMON_YEAR for fetch only optimize for 100 rows
